{
  "style": "IEEE",
  "texts": [
    "Since AI has exhibited creative potential particularly in finding diverse visual inspiration, there is a growing trend of integrating AI into design ideation CSTs.",
    "For instance, SemanticCollage [36] has a semantic search feature that uses AI-recognized semantic labels to support both visual and semantic-based ideation.",
    "Their work shows that semantic labels can support more holistic design exploration and reflection within the ideation process.",
    "ImageSense further combines semantic search and AI-suggested images in a collaborative moodboard [35].",
    "In their work, designers build digital moodboards in a human-human-AI collaborative setting, while the AI analyses the moodboard content to find new (existing) image suggestions."
  ],
  "correct_citations": [
    "For instance, SemanticCollage [36] has a semantic search feature that uses AI-recognized semantic labels to support both visual and semantic-based ideation.",
    "ImageSense further combines semantic search and AI-suggested images in a collaborative moodboard [35]."
  ]
}